1. *Skoči* visoko i uhvati loptu. (Jump* up high* and catch the ball.)
2. Videla sam da si *skočio* kada je zazvonio telefon. (I saw that you *jumped* when the phone rang.)
3. Ako ne *skočiš* sada, propustićeš priliku. (If you don't *jump* now, you'll miss the opportunity.)
4. Ova mačka može da *skoči* na krov. (This cat can *jump* onto the roof.)
5. On *skoči* u vodu i zaplivao do druge strane bazena. (He *jumped* into the water and swam to the other side of the pool.)
6. Moramo *skočiti* u voz koji kreće za pet minuta. (We have to *jump* onto the train leaving in five minutes.)
7. Kada vidiš vatru, prvo *skoči* u bazen. (When you see fire, first *jump* into the pool.)
8. Uspela sam da *skočim* preko prepreke i završim trku na prvom mestu. (I managed to *jump* over the obstacle and finish the race in first place.)
9. Koliko visoko možeš *skočiti*? (How high can you *jump*?)
10. Moraćeš da *skočiš* odatle ako želiš da uhvatiš autobus. (You'll have to *jump* from there if you want to catch the bus.)